-- 1746 rows across 2 item classes (Capital Goods, Fabric). The
-- export has only Item Class/Category Name/Short Name/Name/HSN Code — HSN
-- Code is blank throughout and left null. UOM (Base/Stock/Billing/Planning/
-- Purchase, always identical to each other per row in the source PDF) is
-- defaulted per item class (NOS / KGS) with per-category overrides derived
-- from direct PDF spot-checks where a category showed mixed UOM. Blocked
-- (is_active) defaults to active for all rows; Created User/Dt are not in
-- the export and are set to a placeholder admin + import time rather than
-- fabricated, matching the tradeoff already made for 0290 Categories.
-- Remaining item classes (Garments Coordinates, General, Packing
-- Accessories, Sewing Accessories) are out of scope pending a follow-up
-- export. Idempotent (not-exists guard on item_class_id + code, since
-- Short Name is confirmed unique within each item class in this dataset).
-- ============================================================================

